title: Albert Schweitzer plays Bach Organ Works
description:
Albert Schweitzer plays Bach Organ Works
at Parish Church, Gunsbach, Alsace.

Columbia-Odyssey Album 32 16 003 / LP 32 26 0063

Tracklist:

Record 1:
 Side 1: 
  1. Prelude in C major, BWV 531
  2,3,4. Toccata, adagio and fugue in C major, BWV 564
 Side 2:
  1. Fugue in A minor, BWV 543
  2. Fantasia and fugue in G minor "The Great", BWV 542

Record 2:
 Side 1:
  1. Prelude in D major, BWV 532
  2. Canzona in D minor, BWV 588
  3. Choral Prelude, BWV 639
  4. Choral Prelude, BWV 668
 Side 2:
  1,2. Choral Prelude, BWV 622 (two versions)
  3. Choral Prelude, BWV 604
  4. Choral Prelude, BWV 727
  5. Choral Prelude, BWV 659

Bonus: Bach-Busoni - Choral Prelude, BWV 659 (piano)
